Bob SW,<br><br>
Thanks for your response. I too have come to accept that there will be wars. <br><br>
These days there is a growing appreciation for our men and women in uniform, and this is good. They, the ones who protest us, always have it in the backs of their minds that -at a moment's notice - they could be sent to fight and die for our country.<br><br>
Ed,<br><br>
I have always appreciated your support and friendship. A while ago you claimed to see in only black and white. My opinion is that you are one of the most open minded people on this site. You have strong convictions of your own, yet are still willing to recognize the need in others to have strong convictions of their own - even if they differ.<br><br>
Art,<br><br>
What can I say? You have a knack for bringing the best out in others. Thanks for you kindness.<br><br>
I'm pulling for you in your battle with PTSD. Only you know what it will take to whip it. Don't ever quit.<br><br>
Cook,<br><br>
